    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Research, study, teaching, publication, and other dissemination of information in the humanities that is mediated through digital technology. It is an evolving area of study, using computing technologies to investigate questions and areas of research that are both traditional and new to the humanities.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
